{"tid":1564733,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"話商場唱歌係走向雨革失敗根本係過份擔心","createTime":"2019-09-13T01:24:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T06:29:22.000Z","uid":29006,"like":111,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"20b66e84a936921b595df6b3b8f948a68d5574f4","tid":1564733,"uid":29006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:24:58.000Z","msg":"當年失敗係因為每次吹雞都係去到抗爭地點(金鐘) 一齊乜都唔做，紥營、打邊爐、唱「今天我」。<br />\n<br />\n到咗今日勇武手足上晒力，日日都Stand by做抗爭，你<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>以為大家喺商場唱吓歌就會令班勇武手足唔再勇武，返去陪大家一齊唱歌?</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n唱歌呢個活動係畀無勇氣、無能力掟磚放火嘅手足去<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">幫勇武手足打支強心針嘅絕佳活動</span></strong>，唱歌話畀勇武手足知<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港市民無放棄你哋</span></strong>，勇武手足望返去後面會見到有班人一直支持你咃。<br />\n<br />\n何況，每次喺商場都見到有好多夜媽媽仲著緊校服嘅學生同大家一齊唱一齊嗌，有啲係幾個後生仔成身汗著住運動裝，似係操完身體同大家一齊唱。有好多人仲訓練緊自己去上前線，一班淨係睇直播就犬儒上身嘅人，試吓落多啲示威現場，落多啲商場睇吓發生緊咩事，唔好一見到唔啱心水就散佈失敗主義好無?<br />\n<br />\n光復香港  時代革命"},{"pid":"d879132a5eff30c128c5af2ebf0779d1258f46c1","tid":1564733,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:25:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"d545d148150f255e4fc9132714b735a58e447795","tid":1564733,"uid":29006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:27:22.000Z",