例如唱歌同10點鳩叫至少令呢一大班人覺得自己仲係呢一場抗爭入面，起碼keep到個心態。鬼唔知200萬大一齊勇武就可以收政府皮咩，但現實就係冇咁多人同你一齊勇武丫麻，咪惟有推和理非一步一步咁行快d囉！連全民跳閘都做唔到既時候，點樣期望全民勇武呢？<br />\n<br />\n最緊要係大家都係keep住參與，閒日和理非d,星期六日就勇武d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"911f123f82f0011c5dd6535c471b325fe1b51ec0","tid":1564733,"uid":9049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:47:19.000Z","msg":"Push <br />\n@期望連仔幫手壓制fake news <br />\n@上連登要用多用腦！<br />\n最新活動：唱民主聖歌，傳福音！<br />\n杯葛黨鐵商場：齋睇唔買，儲多d錢！<br />\n913中秋賞燈晚會，附近連儂牆見！<br />\n連儂牆戰線不能倒！修建連儂，有你有我<br />\n<ins>考驗毅力與堅持</ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">做更具價值嘅野</span><br />\n<br />\n#離開同溫層，接觸各種人，理解佢地嘅想法，將不支持我們的人轉為支持我們！這是成功的方法！<br />\n<br />\n@Template@<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />抗爭/革命搞十年八載唔出奇<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">衛城革命，生活抗爭；拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗；</span><br />\n<em>每日任務：</em><br />\n1. 優先<span style=\"color: red;\">幫襯</span>良心商店<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">抵制</span>「邪惡」「無良」的商戶，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶、減少八達通<br />\n3. 安全之下，<span style=\"color: red;\">免費港鐵</span>；二人同遊，一人免費；買平飛；長者八達通<br />\n4. 夜晚<span style=\"color: red;\">十點咆哮</span>！（改9點會少好多人）<br />\n5. <span style=\"color: red;\">健身+運動</span>，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n6. <span style=\"color: red;\">每日一post</span>，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest #Chinazi<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests <br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmDYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=b4368561\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n7. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n8. 保持<span style=\"color: red;\">獨立思考</span>，分析能力level up，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">冷處理fake news/ rumour</span></strong> 、五毛分化post<br />\n<br />\n<em>每星期任務：</em><br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">低消費</span>，高儲蓄；罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">做孝子救港</span>，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去<span style=\"color: red;\">連儂牆</span>貼3張文宣，輸出革命思想<br />\n<br />\n<em>每月任務：</em><br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股，MPF都買美股<br />\n2. 搵多一個人參與<br />\n3. 關心社會、陪審員、派傳單、放映會<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾；Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.13 @Template End@"},{"pid":"5885fcc2e2ac091883d6eb5cf9074f78016da4f2","tid":1564733,"uid":83062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"774082c67e0bdd020717a9f7b8fc6ac22e7efb4a","tid":1564733,"uid":29006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3647d4df44959056e70170d59ca7a72d224f5d30","tid":1564733,"uid":298077,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:28:05.000Z","msg":"啱 次次宣傳埋行動  915 維園見<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔明d人點解會話失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:31:07.000Z","msg":"理解佢哋嘅憂慮，但咁樣過份擔心其實同終極和理非擔心玩吓火就會失民心有咩分別?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:47:50.000Z","msg":"冷氣軍師係咁"},{"pid":"bdeec33f0834dc18975655f847a94b63e3d6c32a","tid":1564733,"uid":74888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5885fcc2e2ac091883d6eb5cf9074f78016da4f2","tid":1564733,"uid":83062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"774082c67e0bdd020717a9f7b8fc6ac22e7efb4a","tid":1564733,"uid":29006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3647d4df44959056e70170d59ca7a72d224f5d30","tid":1564733,"uid":298077,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:28:05.000Z","msg":"啱 次次宣傳埋行動  915 維園見<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔明d人點解會話失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:31:07.000Z","msg":"理解佢哋嘅憂慮，但咁樣過份擔心其實同終極和理非擔心玩吓火就會失民心有咩分別?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:47:50.000Z","msg":"冷氣軍師係咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:53:04.000Z","msg":"唔係話